    "notes": [
      "Three-player JS/Python canary for same-frame point materialization before a lower-index avatar's body-collision phase.",
      "Source update order is p2, then p1, then p0. p1 starts printing, emits a point at (41.6,40) during Avatar.update, and Game.onPoint inserts the collision body immediately.",
      "p0 then moves to the same endpoint in the same Game.update frame and dies to p1's newly inserted body.",
      "Forced trail state makes initial printing a direct setup state and avoids setup-time printManager.start() body insertion."
    ]
  },
